## CSS Standards

### Evolution Timeline Styling
```css
.evolution-timeline {
  margin: 2rem 0;
}

.timeline-container {
  position: relative;
  padding-left: 2rem;
}

.timeline-marker.completed {
  background: #4caf50;
}

.timeline-marker.active {
  background: #2196f3;
  animation: pulse 2s infinite;
}

.timeline-marker.planned {
  background: #9e9e9e;
}
```

### Navigation Styling
```css
.evolution-navigation {
  background: #f8f9fa;
  border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 1.5rem;
  margin: 2rem 0;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
  gap: 2rem;
}
```

### Context Styling
```css
.evolution-context {
  background: #e3f2fd;
  border-left: 4px solid #2196f3;
  padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
  margin: 1.5rem 0;
  border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
}
```

## Content Standards

### Post Structure
1. **Evolution Context**: Include evolution information at post start
2. **Navigation**: Include previous/next evolution links
3. **Content**: Main post content
4. **Key Learnings**: What was learned and why
5. **Cross-References**: Link to related posts

### Evolution Pages
1. **Overview**: Evolution description and goals
2. **Posts**: List of posts in this evolution
3. **Navigation**: Previous/next evolution links
4. **Key Learnings**: What was learned in this evolution

### Project Hub
1. **Overview**: Project description and philosophy
2. **Timeline**: Visual evolution progression
3. **Navigation**: Links to all evolutions and posts
4. **Metrics**: Current status and statistics

